criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1) relationship between allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation of healthy donors;
2) aged 18-55 years;
3) weight 50-100Kg;
4) normal heart function;
5) normal liver and kidney function;
6) hepatitis index examination negative;
7) detection of cytomegalovirus negative;
8) normal ECG;
9) ultrasound of abdomen, chest normal;
10) Voluntary participants, informed consent.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1) Uncontrolled active infection;
2) unrelated allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation;
3) HIV antibody, syphilis antibody positive;
4) with allergic diseases or allergies, or of the goods or other genetically engineered Escherichia coli derived from biological products allergy;
5) serious spirit or nervous system disorders, effects of informed consent and/or adverse reaction statement or observation;
6) in lactation.
